## Attach Agent to Workspace

```shell
## Create and assign agent to Workspace
curl -X "POST" "<%= config[:base_url] %>/workspaces/<ID>/create-agent" \
     -H 'x-api-key: <%= config[:api_key] %>' \\
     -H 'tio-auth-token: <%= config[:api_token] %>' \\
     -H 'Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json' \\
     -d $'{
  "data": {
    "type": "users",
    "attributes": {
      "user-name": "hucicogo@gerla.org",
      "first-name": "Hunter",
      "last-name": "Watson",
      "login-provider": "EMAIL"
    }
  }
}'
```

This endpoint creates an agent in a specific workspace.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config[:base_url]%>/workspaces/<ID>/create-agent`

### BODY Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
user-name | The login name of the agent. This should be an email address
first-name | The first name of the agent
last-name | The last name of the agent
login-provider | The strategy to be used for login. Usually a SAML provider


## Assign Agent to Additional Workspace

```shell
curl -X "PUT" "<%= config[:base_url] %>/workspaces/<ID>/assign-agent" \
     -H 'x-api-key: <%= config[:api_key] %>' \\
     -H 'tio-auth-token: <%= config[:api_token] %>' \\
     -H 'Content-Type: application/vnd.api+json' \\
     -d $'{
  "data": {
  "type": "workspaces",
  "id": "<ID>",
  "relationships": {
    "user": {
       "type": "users",
       "id": "<AGENT_ID>"
     }
  }
  }
}'
```

This endpoint assigns an agent in an additional workspace.

`POST <%= config[:base_url]%>/workspaces/<ID>/assign-agent`
